high_descs: Turn to the right and then the right again. Find the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge and take out the apple. Shut the door.
Take the apple and turn to the left and left again to get to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the apple inside. Shut the door and then open it again and take out the apple. Shut the door.
Take the apple and turn to the left and left again to face the island.
Place the apple on the counter, in between the two loaves of bread.
anns.task_desc: Heat an apple and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Take an apple out of the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Turn and go to the counter by the oven.
Put the apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple on the counter by the oven.

high_descs: Turn right and go around the kitchen island to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take out the apple from inside.
Turn left to go around the kitchen island until you reach the microwave, above the dishwasher.
Open the microwave, put the apple inside and heat it, then take it out.
Turn left and move forward, then turn left to face the kitchen island.
Place the apple on the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple on the kitchen island.
